e peaks are generic by proposing a theoretically\npossible mechanism but also explains why these hypothesized conditions are\nnaturally satisfied in experiments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Oct 2021 17:00:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Oct 2021 21:04:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 30 Mar 2022 23:17:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-01"}
