t ratio -- and thus the statistical modeling of\ncoherent structures in the ASL -- are highly sensitive to the value of the\nstability parameter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Oct 2021 19:49:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-08"}
