(i.e., going towards ideal MHD), the\npeeling-ballooning modes that constrain the pedestal below the type-I ELM\nstability boundary display sharply decreasing growth rates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Oct 2021 07:48:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
