equence of 10 plasma treatments (upon 2\nmin) separated by short stirring procedures leads to a gain in vigor as high as\n405 min vs 275 min for a single plasma treatment of 20 min. We propose to\nunderstand these results by correlating the gain in vigor with the water uptake\nof the seeds and the wettability state of their coating.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 15 Oct 2021 13:25:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-20"}
